Examining GDS_deep2_5692

GDS_deep2_5692 is has a human classification of:

  • Spheroid:0.0
  • Disk:0.7
  • Irregular:0.3
  • Point Source:0.0

    To get the classification for a src within a segmap, we calculate the following: $$\frac{\sum_i (1-bkg_i)m_{ji} / \sigma^2_{m_ji}}{\sum_i(1-bkg_i)/\sigma^2_{m_ji}} $$ Where \(i\) represents a pixel in the segmap assocaited with a source and $$m \in {Spheroid, Disk, Point Source, Irregular}$$ After the value for each class is calculated, it is renormalized to sum to 1
